```

This tells the system the output should be parsed by the PEG parser defined in `data.parser`.

### **8. COMMON_CHAT_PARAMS STRUCT (chat.h, lines 177-190)**

```cpp
struct common_chat_params {
    common_chat_format                  format = COMMON_CHAT_FORMAT_CONTENT_ONLY;
    std::string                         prompt;
